snippet.title: Leucanthemum Eyes | Short Horror Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Daisy went into a tunnel to wait out the rain, but suddenly ended up waking up in a sewer... or something similar to a sewer, but hellish.
Daisy needs to escape this place.

(A short point and click game made in ren'py, inspired by DreadOut and Silent Hill)

Download:
https://kuraishimi.itch.io/leucanthemum-eyes
